// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2479 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: d2e0b4a8-a630-5c76-87ba-dc200059cea9

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:12.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.04*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:14.10*")
